task.summary: Implement new generic Pool to replace lots of identical code.
Add AccessibleMember.setFlag() to set raw access flag
Add ByteStream.readFully to fully read the stream
Add Remapper ClassVisitor implementation for remapping class references
Add signature validation in SignatureReader, throws VerifyError
Create Metadatable interface to replace Pool<Attribute> level fetching
Add a proper add visitors varargs
Add WIP XMLAttribute for storing arbitrary values (i.e. a HashMap) as an attribute
Removed incremental loading and updated Metadatable implementation
Added benchmark test: JBL, ASM, BCEL, and SERP
Bulleted lists look nicer than code tags
Remove Signature & SourceFile attributes by adding a case to Metadatable.Container
Removed ConstantValue, Signature, and SourceFile attributes
Make pool getter names more concise
Refactor visitors to be easier to auto-implement in smart IDEs
